  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Establishing gauge invariant linear response of fermionic superfluids with pair fluctuations: A diagrammatic approach</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="c">2017-03-15</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• We have developed a gauge invariant linear response theory which can be applied to the whole BCS-BEC crossover. • We construct an external U(1) field vertex which satisfies the Ward identity by a diagrammatic method. • Both the effects of the collective modes of broken U(1) symmetry and the pair fluctuations are consistently considered.</subfield>
